# Goals & Dreams Engine

See [GOALS_DREAMS_ENGINE.md](../../GOALS_DREAMS_ENGINE.md).

## Rules

1. Support aspirations — never create guilt or pressure around setbacks.
2. Business logic in Supabase RPCs; panels and API routes are thin clients.
3. Natural language goal detection requires user confirmation before `create_user_goal`.
4. Vague goals trigger clarification — never assume specifics silently.
5. Milestones auto-suggested on creation; user can complete, pause, or archive.
6. Celebrations and check-ins respect `gde_settings` toggles.
7. Platform uses `get_platform_goals_overview` — aggregates only, never goal content.
8. i18n: `customerApp.goalsDreams.*`, `platform.goalsDreams.*` in en/no/sv/da.

## Tables

`gde_settings` · `user_goals` · `goal_milestones` · `goal_actions` · `goal_activity`

## Route

`/app/assistant/goals`
